title: Joe Zawinul - Stories Of The Danube (1996) [EAC-FLAC]
description:
1. The Beginning (05:49)
In the depths of the forest a spring wells up: a river is born.
2. Mountain Waters (03:30)
Waterfalls of melted snow cascade into the young river.
3. Empire (11:22)
An impression of life in the reign of Emperor Franz Joseph at the turn of the century.
4. Intro (03:52)
5. Gypsy (07:35)
History of a free people without a home.
6. Voice Of The Danube (05:53)
On the riverbed, an imposing rock watches history flowing by.
7. Unknown Soldier (10:25)
A stream of blood and violence: the Second World War.
